1) Permission request (important)
--------------------------------
GitHub may allow users to view and fork this repository within the GitHub website.
However, permission is required from the author BEFORE you:
- publish your own modified version,
- distribute modified files,
- make a public fork intended for development (pull requsts),
- use this code in another project,
- re-upload this addon anywhere else.

If you want to fork or modify: please contact the author first and ask. The reason for this is to keep a source of truth for users, and ask contributors to rather create pull requests for development purposes.


2) Allowed use
-------------
You may download and use DoiteAuras for personal in-game purposes.


3) No redistribution / no modified releases
